Text:
Whenever I mount Shivers it tells me I need to install it, but when I do it sends me an error message:

C;\Windows\system32\autoexec.nt. The system file is not suitable for running msdos and microsoft windows applications. choose close to terminate the application.

I've gone to a few sites which break down what I have to do but none of them fixed anything. Anyone know how I can fix this?
